<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-82-0016 </DOCNO><TEXT>21 papers deal with the fundamental statistics of acoustic standardizationdiscussing the different uses of methods in the case of household appliances,computer and business equipment, processing machinery, gearings, machinetools and chemical plants. Some of the papers are dedicated to the evaluationof noise measurement, automatic acoustic measuring systems and soundemission measurement.</TEXT></DOC>